node.title: R훮hui placed at Whakat훮ne after drowning
node.description: A r훮hui is in place for the Whakat훮ne heads after a drowning there last night.
node.content:
["A r\u0101hui is in place for the Whakat\u0101ne heads after a drowning there last night.", "", "
\nPhoto: Unsplash / Jackson Currie\n
", "People are being asked not to use or gather seafood from an area that stretches from the Whakat\u0101ne river mouth to near, but not including, West End Beach at \u014chope.", "The r\u0101hui, which will be lifted on Thursday, includes the popular \u014ctarawairere Bay.", "Ng\u0101ti Awa chair Joe Harawira said it was a mark of respect to the family of the person who drowned at the heads."]
